th-sphere gas. A comparison with some preliminary\nsimulation results shows a very good agreement for conditions of practical\ninterest.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 29 Jan 2018 15:53:34 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 9 May 2018 14:54:40 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-05-10"}
